WEBVTT

00:01:28.833 --> 00:01:31.351
But we know that we have
to make this happen,

00:01:31.375 --> 00:01:35.809
because if not, we will never have time
to be able to volunteer

00:01:35.833 --> 00:01:39.833
to help on these many causes
that are now facing us.

00:01:41.333 --> 00:01:44.184
One of the areas that women
can give up a little bit of time

00:01:44.208 --> 00:01:46.184
and that is in shopping, OK?

00:01:46.208 --> 00:01:48.726
(Laughter)

00:01:48.750 --> 00:01:50.434
And especially when we go out there

00:01:50.458 --> 00:01:52.559
shopping for things
that we don't even need.

00:01:52.583 --> 00:01:53.601
(Laughter)

00:01:53.625 --> 00:01:57.351
You know, you never saw
a hearse with a U-Haul behind it.

00:01:57.375 --> 00:02:00.393
(Laughter)